Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:03.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,"February 13th"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.33,0:00:04.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,"February 14th"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come for my chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was promised chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're talking about Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that. Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you hear that from?\NDo we even have any chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like some chocolate from you, too, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Sure, if you give me some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's how Valentine's works.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:47.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,I think so! Take that, and that, and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I shall prepare some\Nfor you the next time we meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yipee!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This happens every time, so there's\Na part of me that just expects it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:00:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:01:04.77,OS,,0,0,0,,"Does tomorrow work for you?\NCan you still hang out?"\N"I sure can."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Shimamura started hibernating\Nin her {\i1}kotatsu {\i0}and won't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:21.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Kay, thanks!" "Sure!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:22.83,OS,,0,0,0,,"Kay, thanks!"\N"Sure!"\N"Morning!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:24.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Morning!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one look at Shimamura warms my heart.\NNo wonder she's my sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,We have an English quiz today, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,Ayup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,You two seem confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured if I kept calling her that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd eventually be less embarrassing, but it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.10,On Top,,0,0,0,,Let me see your notes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Chocolate already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought it, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I get it, but now I feel like\NI'm being told to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...basically Shimamura's puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I mean, if I was a pup,\Nmaybe Shimamura would hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I could curl up on her lap...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And she'd do all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Being Shimamura's pup would be like the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been pretty unfortunate up until now,\Nbut now I know for certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually pretty stupid lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to go hang out now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there somewhere you wanted to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I want to go to Nagoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... Um... Is that a bit too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's how this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are we going to do in Nagoya, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy some chocolate.\NUm... I haven't bought any yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just thought it'd be fresher\Nif I bought some the day of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see. Well, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Maybe Shimamura's\Nmore excited than I thought she'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I see her smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, your chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get to see it until you buy yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I gave you yours now, it wouldn't\Nbe an exchange, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I really am just Shimamura's puppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:06:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to change into\Nyour Chinese dress today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like you did on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd rather have me wear that,\NI'll go change...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, if you want me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I mean, we don't want to leave too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Limited Express" "Toyohashi"\NSpecial Rapid Train" "Toyohashi"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! We'll make the train if we run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now time for a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprise you knew the transfer time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:42.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,The train bound for Toyohashi\Nis now departing from lane four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful of the closing doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it... Though just barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's an open seat. Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take it, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can have it, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you should sit, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sleeping during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you really were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, I guess I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Does... my face look weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So... It's about 20 minutes to Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty boring until then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah... Then why don't we play {\i1}shiritori{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiritori{\i0}? Nice. In that case... Apple [{\i1}ringo{\i0}]!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go? Go... {\i1}Gomoku {\i0}soba{\i1}.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you are a kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ba... Ba... Basketball [{\i1}basuketobooru{\i0}].
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ru... Ru... {\i1}Ruibe{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ruibe{\i0}? Seriously, Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... Ice cream [{\i1}aisu{\i0}].
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Su... Su... Su...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Five... Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Su?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Love [{\i1}suki{\i0}].
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.19,On Top,,0,0,0,,Two... One.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Su... Su... Sugyaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Su... Su... Su... Sugakiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you just said it too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sugakiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagoya, Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make sure to take all of your...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, there's a huge line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I line up, I'm just going\Nto make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... There's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should we do next to kill some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um... M-Maybe thumb wrestle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleven victories and three losses. I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, thumb wrestling can get pretty heated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura seems to be all smiles today,\Nwhich is throwing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I see her smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stop my cheek muscles\Nfrom relaxing into a dumb expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's the big reveal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Your Valentine's chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually bought some from here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:26.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,"February 14th"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,"February 13th"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening. Wait, I guess it's still hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you have something you wanted to shop for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Do you have a boyfriend, Shima?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just getting some to give to a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The train bound for Toyohashi\Nis about to depart from lane four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful of the closing doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We just made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, just barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's one seat open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,Why don't you sit, Shima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So... You're in high school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see my uniform and bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess you're in high school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. Have you actually\Nbeen going to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhat. Looks like you need\Nto redye your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I've been trying to decide\Nwhat to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Shima...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you call me when we were little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shima! Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima, you've really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:13:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Change is an understatement.\NI was basically a stranger before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be insanely cheerful, super friendly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,dumb, and free...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's what Tarumi\Nexpects me to be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, remember when there was a murder here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the big city scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why being with Tarumi\Nis honestly a bit uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's slightly different,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but I sorta feel like Adachi right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Reality doesn't change\Nas gracefully as memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually bought some from here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, reall--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, let's exchange chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Congrats?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:14:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then, uh... Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just let them sit in your room.\NMake sure you eat them, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then let's eat them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, now? Right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you don't waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess you're telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:15:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way to make her doubt me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you want one, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, say, "Ah."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:16:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It should start around 6 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What will?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:09.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Special Valentine's Day Promotion"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting! Let's go, Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:12.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,"We'll share your messages"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:17.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,"I love you, Kazuki!! Forever! -Makiko"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.60,On Top,,0,0,0,,"I love you, Take!\N- Mizu"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:31.86,On Top,,0,0,0,,"I hope we can continue to stay close"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we were expecting this\Nto be a lot more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There were probably more things\Nthat should've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But in reality, all that remains\Nis this bothersome heavy mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:15.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Does tomorrow work for you?\NCan you still hang out?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:23.54,OS,,0,0,0,,"Does tomorrow work for you?\NCan you still hang out?"\N"I sure can."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:24.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,"I sure can."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drag you around today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something so lingering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Something incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you supposed to do at times like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you call me when we were little?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Hrm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it! Listen to me, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let go of the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,People can't change that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:35.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,"I hope we can continue to stay close!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My past is connected by briars,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so when I try to reflect upon it,\NI'm hurt by my incomplete self from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:44.04,On Top,,0,0,0,,"-Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times I want to reach into the briars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:49.04,On Top,,0,0,0,,"I hope we can continue to stay close!\N- Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that means I prick myself and bleed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:56.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,"I hope we can continue to stay close!\N- Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:19:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura... Wait, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this fortunetelling bit\Non this nightly TV program.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They were asking for entries,\Nso I tried sending it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Libra"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lucky letter is... D!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I'd never see it,\Nso I put something mild... Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:21.07,On Top,,0,0,0,,"I hope we can continue to stay close!\N- Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already over? That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What exactly did you mean by close?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What did I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Did you need an actual example?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering, like,\Nwhat kind of direction you meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think it was perfect to see this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was entering this thing,\Nyour face popped into my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:03.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,"I'll make you fall for me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tried to reflect that into my message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's... wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you just startled me. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no more surprise glomps, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I can then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:21:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So... If I ask you first,\Nit's okay, to uh, do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You want to hug me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well... Because it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever! Come get some! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I guess this is one way to get closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:22:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Though you're so skinny, Adachi,\Nthat neither one of us are going to get warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if everyone around us\Nthought we were weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they laughing at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I could only see Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Any place I could do that made it the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:22.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 9: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:24:06.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Next Time: 'Cherry Blossoms and\NSpring and Spring and the Moon'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.83,0:23:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji's Butcher Shop is doing\Na Valentine's Day promotion, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:23:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You selling chocolate-filled croquettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing that cliché.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab your boy's heart with\Na special on actual hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you feel getting offal from a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.29,0:24:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fire up that grill!
